<plot>Three women come to Terezin, formerly known as the concentration camp "Theresienstadt", searching for trails of Karel Svenk. He was called "Chaplin of Theresinenstadt" because he played Cabaret there until his deportation to Auschwitz. They find survivors of the holocaust who met Svenk and still know his songs.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?149845</url></doc>
